quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By the panting chargers
  100,2,by the strikers of sparks
  100,3,by the raiders at dawn
  100,4,raising thereby a trail of dust
  100,5,penetrating to the center altogether
  100,6,truly man is ungrateful to his Lord
  100,7,and truly he is a witness to that
  100,8,and truly he is fierce in his love for good things
  100,9,Does he not know that when what lies within graves is turned inside out
  100,10,and what lies within breasts is made known
  100,11,truly on that Day their Lord shall be aware of them